summary: Full Cubase AI6 project for \"Sons of Skyrim\" & \"The Dragonborn Comes\" cover makers. Includes 16 vocal lines, midi lines (chords & melodies) and CD-quality \"wave\" track. Project settings are 24Kbit&48Khz wave audio. You can use my project for free for making your covers, just add \"based on CHUR\'s (http://chur.ho.ua/) Cubase AI6 project\"
descriptionHtml: Full Cubase AI6 project for \"Sons of Skyrim\" & \"The Dragonborn Comes\" songs cover makers. Includes 16 vocal lines, midi lines (chords & melodies) and CD-quality \"wave\" track. Project settings are 24Kbit&48Khz wave audio. You can use my project for free for making your covers, just add \"based on CHUR\'s (http://chur.ho.ua/) Cubase AI6 project\" and, of course, note the author of music - Jeremy Soule composer. Cubase 6 sequensor available for free at official Steinberg page http://www.steinberg.net/en/products/cubase/trial_version.html
author: CHUR
